It has 2 bdrm, full bath, living room and kitchen upstairs and one bedroom, full bath, laundry room and a den downstairs. It is a great location, close to the Indian Head Naval Base, the water with fishing pier and boat ramp and the Village Green. Section 8 okay. No Pets.

Description: This is a must see spacious 3 bedroom end-unit townhome w/attached garage. Master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and master bath with huge shower and his and hers shower heads. Also, approximately 30 minutes to National Harbor!

Description: Serving Enlisted Personnel, E01-E09, the Riverview Village community was built in 2010 and is within walking distance of the Indian Head Naval Base. Riverview Village offers home for all sizes of families and several ADA adaptive residences are also available. Each three- to four-bedroom home includes the very latest in kitchen appliances, carpeting, central air, fenced in backyards, and two-car garages. Neighborhood amenities include a pool, a playground, a dog park, basketball and tennis courts, and the popular Tiki Bar for individuals 21 years old and up. The community offers a free gym membership to all active duty military members and their families and provides several community centers for social gatherings. There are many restaurants and shopping opportunities just minutes from the community, along with renowned K-12 schools. With Washington, D.C. just 45 minutes north, the Riverview Village community abounds with cultural and recreational activities for people of all ages.
